WEBVTT

00:08:56.933 --> 00:09:00.620
But then he said,
"I hate going to Asia or ..."

00:09:00.644 --> 00:09:04.087
and he mentioned a particular country,
Asia and some of these countries.

00:09:04.111 --> 00:09:08.134
"They keep me for this, trying
to get the best deal for their countries.

00:09:08.158 --> 00:09:09.334
They get the best deal.

00:09:09.358 --> 00:09:12.266
They tell me, 'Oh,
that clause will not work for us

00:09:12.290 --> 00:09:13.897
in our environment.

00:09:13.921 --> 00:09:16.894
It's not our reality.
It's just so Western.'

00:09:16.918 --> 00:09:20.029
And they tell me, 'Oh,
we have enough experts

00:09:20.053 --> 00:09:21.256
to take care of this.

00:09:21.280 --> 00:09:22.901
You don't have enough experts.

00:09:22.925 --> 00:09:24.078
We know our aim.'

00:09:24.102 --> 00:09:26.547
And they just keep going
through all these things.

00:09:26.571 --> 00:09:29.091
By the time they finish,
yes, they get the best deal,

00:09:29.115 --> 00:09:32.280
but I'm so exhausted and I don't get
the best deal for the bank,